As an Associate Community Manager at Likeable Media, you will help respond to and engage with large, enthusiastic brand communities. This is your chance to spend all day on Facebook--and get paid for it. You will work alongside our full-time Community Managers, gaining hands-on, real world agency experience (the kind that will make your friends jealous). You will be given amazing networking opportunities and mentored by some real social media pros, learning the skills that can&rsquo;t be taught in a classroom. We&rsquo;re flexible with your work schedule, and expect you to be as well.</p>
<p>
<strong>Expectations:</strong> This is not a typical internship. We&rsquo;re looking for <u><strong>students</strong></u> who attend NYC area schools,&nbsp; are willing to commute to the city, and can work 15 hours per week (including some weekend and evening work). There is a monthly stipend and college credit can be earned.</p>
